snippet.title: Jupiter Moons: Mecha - "Revenge of the spiders" trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for Jupiter Moons: Mecha
Wishlist ➡ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1288540/Jupiter_Moons_Mecha?utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=trailer

Choose your mech, customize your loadout, and build your perfect deck. Experiment with cards to find powerful combinations as you enjoy the tactical combat and deckbuilding in this roguelike adventure!

If you want to learn more, check:

* Discord - https://discord.gg/sHNysXG

* Reddit - https://www.reddit.com/r/RockAndBushes/
